  <para style="h">Fịlịmọn</para>
  <para style="toc1">Fịlịmọn</para>
  <para style="toc2">Fịlịmọn</para>
  <para style="toc3">Fịl</para>
  <para style="mt1">Fịlịmọn</para>
  <para style="mt4">(Pọl dere ya nʼafọ 60 maọbụ 61 mgbe a mụsịrị Kraịst)</para>
  <para style="imt">Ihe dị nʼime ya</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ihe dị nʼime ya:</para>
  <para style="im">Onisimọs bụ otu nʼime ndị ohu Fịlịmọn. Ma o sitere nʼụlọ nna ya ukwu gbapụ gbaga Rom. Nʼebe ahụ ka Pọl zutere ya kwusaara ya oziọma Kraịst. Onisimọs chegharịrị ghọọ onye Kraịst. Emesịa, Onisimọs kpebiri ịlaghachikwuru nna ya ukwu. Nʼihi ya Pọl deere Fịlịmọn akwụkwọ a ịrịọ ya ka ọ gbaghara Onisimọs ma nabatakwa ya dị ka nwanna ya nʼime Kraịst.</para>
  <para style="iot">Usoro e si dee ya:</para>
  <para style="io1">Ekele Pọl <char style="ior"><ref loc="PHM 1:1-3">1-3</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Ndụ ọma Fịlịmọn <char style="ior"><ref loc="PHM 1:4-7">4-7</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Arịrịọ Pọl nʼisi Onisimọs <char style="ior"><ref loc="PHM 1:8-22">8-22</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Okwu mmechi <char style="ior"><ref loc="PHM 1:23-25">23-25</ref></char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="PHM 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="PHM 1:1"/>Pọl, onye e tinyere nʼụlọ mkpọrọ nʼihi Kraịst Jisọs na site nʼaka nwanna anyị Timoti,</para>
  <para style="b" vid="PHM 1:1"/>
  <para style="p" vid="PHM 1:1">Anyị na-edetara gị ya ezi enyi anyị na onye anyị na ya na-arụkọ ọrụ, Fịlịmọn. <verse eid="PHM 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="PHM 1:2"/>Anyị na-edetakwara ya nzukọ Kraịst dị nʼụlọ gị, na nwanna anyị nwanyị Afịa, na Akipos onye anyị na ya so na-alụ agha a.<verse eid="PHM 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="PHM 1:3"/>Ka amara na udo nke sitere na Chineke bụ Nna, na Kraịst Jisọs Onyenwe anyị dịrị unu.<verse eid="PHM 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Ekele na ekpere</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="PHM 1:4"/>Ana m ekele Chineke ekele mgbe ọbụla m na-echeta gị nʼekpere niile m na-ekpe. <verse eid="PHM 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="PHM 1:5"/>Nʼihi na ana m anụ ihe banyere okwukwe i nwere nʼime Onyenwe anyị Jisọs, na ịhụnanya i na-egosi ndị nsọ niile. <verse eid="PHM 1:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="PHM 1:6"/>Ekpere m na-ekpe banyere gị bụ ka mmekọrịta anyị na gị dịka ndị kwere ekwe, mee ka ị matazuo ihe ọma niile anyị nwere nʼime Kraịst. <verse eid="PHM 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="PHM 1:7"/>Ịhụnanya gị na-enye m oke ọṅụ na ịgbaume, ezi nwanna m, nʼihi na emeela ka ndị nsọ nwee ume ọhụrụ site nʼinyeaka gị.<verse eid="PHM 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Arịrịọ Pọl nʼisi Onisimọs</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="PHM 1:8"/>Ọ bụ ezie na-enwere m ike nʼime Kraịst inye gị iwu banyere ihe kwesiri ka i mee, ma agaghị m eme otu a. <verse eid="PHM 1:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="PHM 1:9"/>Kama, ọ kaara m mma site na ndabere nke ịhụnanya, ịrịọ gị ya dị ka arịrịọ. Ee, ọ bụ mụ Pọl, agadi nwoke ahụ na onye mkpọrọ nʼihi Kraịst Jisọs na-arịọ gị arịrịọ a. <verse eid="PHM 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="PHM 1:10"/>Biko, arịọ m gị nʼisi Onisimọs, onye e mere ka ọ bụrụ nwa m oge m nọ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ. <verse eid="PHM 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="PHM 1:11"/>Na mbụ, o nweghị uru ọbụla ọ baara gị, ma ugbu a, ọ baara mụ na gị uru.<verse eid="PHM 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="PHM 1:12"/>Ana m ezighachiri gị ya ugbu a, ya bụ, onye bụ obi<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">onye m weere ka onwe m</char></note> m ka m na-ezitere gị. <verse eid="PHM 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="PHM 1:13"/>Ọ gụsịrị m agụụ ike ime ka mụ na ya nọdụ nʼebe a, ka o were ọnọdụ gị na-ejere m ozi ọ bụladị dị ka m nọ na mkpọrọ nʼihi oziọma. <verse eid="PHM 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="PHM 1:14"/>Ma, a chọghị m ime ihe ọbụla na-enwetaghị nkwenye gị, ka ọ ghara ịdị ka i mere obiọma gị na mmanye. Kama, achọrọ m ka i mee ihe si gị nʼobi pụta. <verse eid="PHM 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="PHM 1:15"/>Ma eleghị anya, ọ bụ nʼihi nke a ka eji kewapụ ya nwa oge nta site nʼebe ị nọ, bụ ka i mesịa nweghachi ya ebighị ebi. <verse eid="PHM 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="PHM 1:16"/>Ọ bụghịkwa ohu ọzọ, kama ọ karịrị ohu, maka ọ dịka nwanna a hụrụ nʼanya, ọkachasị nʼebe mụ onwe m nọ, ma ọ ga-abụkwara gị karịchasịa, ma nʼanụ ahụ nakwa nʼime Onyenwe anyị.<verse eid="PHM 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="PHM 1:17"/>Nʼihi nke a, ọ bụrụ na ị gụrụ m dị ka onye nnwekọ ihe, nabata ya dị ka ị ga-esi nabata m. <verse eid="PHM 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="PHM 1:18"/>Biko, ọ bụrụ na o mejọrọ gị nʼụzọ ọbụla, ọ bụrụkwa na o ji ụgwọ ọbụla, gụọ ya dị ka ụgwọ m ji gị. <verse eid="PHM 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="PHM 1:19"/>Mụ bụ Pọl ji aka m dee nke a; aga m akwụghachi gị. Ọ bakwaghị uru ichetara gị ụgwọ i ji m. Nʼihi na ụgwọ i ji m bụ gị onwe gị. <verse eid="PHM 1:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="PHM 1:20"/>Nwanna m, mere m ihe a m na-arịọ gị nʼihi Onyenwe anyị. Mekwa ka obi m dị ọhụrụ nʼime Kraịst. <verse eid="PHM 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="PHM 1:21"/>Olileanya m siri m ike na ị ga-aṅa m ntị, ana m edere gị akwụkwọ a, na ị ga-eme, ma karịakwa ka m rịọrọ.<verse eid="PHM 1:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="PHM 1:22"/>Ihe ọzọkwa, bụ na m chọrọ ka ị kwadoro m ọnụụlọ ebe m ga-anọ dị ka ọbịa ma m bịa, maka enwere m olileanya na a ga-aza ekpere unu ime ka m si nʼebe a pụta bịakwute unu.<verse eid="PHM 1:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="PHM 1:23"/>Epafras, onye mụ na ya nọ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ nʼihi Kraịst Jisọs na-ekele gị.<verse eid="PHM 1:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="PHM 1:24"/>Mak, na Arịstakọs, na Dimas, na Luk, ndị mụ na ha na-arụkọ ọrụ na-ekelekwa unu.<verse eid="PHM 1:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="PHM 1:25"/>Ka amara Onyenwe anyị Jisọs Kraịst dịnyere mmụọ unu.<verse eid="PHM 1:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="PHM 1"/>
